						               													<description>&amp;quot;An exciting adventure game&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You're sailing the South Seas with Pippi and the pirates, on an exciting cruise on Pippi's ship Hoppetossa. While visiting a small island, Pippi's feet start to tingle strangely - it's time for a good old brawl and fight after a long sailing! Challenge the five pirates - Pollus, Hot Tin Pan, Oomalat, Dummerkopfen and cook O'Malley - into a dice duel on the gangplank. You'll also need gold coins from the island to bribe them. If you win the pirate you'll get to push him into the sea - but if you lose, it's YOU who'll end up in the drink, and need to swim back to the island for some more coins from Pippi's famous suitcase! Once you get to the ship itself, you need to face ALL the remaining pirates one after the other - unless you're lucky and they're all swimming already, in which case you win an instant victory and get to hoist the flag in Hoppetossa's mast!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
